        {
          "author": "billwuqin",
          "authorAssociation": "CONTRIBUTOR",
          "body": "The path should be changed into \r\n/ni:network-elements/ni:network-element/ni:components/ni:component/ni:component-id\r\nSee snippet in  https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-ivy-network-inventory-yang/\r\n+--rw components\r\n         +--rw component* [component-id]\r\n           +--rw component-id            string\r\n           +--rw uuid?                   yang:uuid\r\nCan you help fix this in the yang module code.",
          "createdAt": "2024-02-08T14:39:12Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-02-08T14:39:12Z"
        },
